tsm-app (1.1.0-1) stable; urgency=low

  * Add: Addon Versions tab collapsible game-version groups with 180 ms animation,
    top-aligned with fixed collapsed height
  * Add: Addon Versions tab always-visible action buttons: download (fresh install),
    refresh (update), trash (uninstall with confirmation; WTF untouched)
  * Add: Addon Versions tab rotating spinner during download, per-row
  * Add: Addon Versions tab Installed Version and Status dot columns
  * Add: Realm Data tab colored status dot (realms: 2h/6h; regions: 26h/50h)
  * Add: per-row trash icon delete button (always visible, turns red on hover)
  * Add: inline Add Realm panel at bottom of Realm Data tab
  * Add: Refresh Now replaced with icon-only button; tooltip shows rate-limit countdown
  * Change: Settings > General Realms section removed; moved to Realm Data tab
  * Change: main window min width raised to 740 px; max width constraint removed
  * Fix: status bar timestamp now updates on every poll; previously frozen
    when realm_statuses was empty (AppHelper not yet detected, etc.)
  * Add: Backups tab per-row restore (green on hover) and delete (red on hover) icon buttons
  * Add: Backups tab Name column with ellipsis; bottom name input (alphanum/hyphen/space,
    max 40 chars) embeds name in filename; Auto=gray tag, Manual=orange tag, uniform width
  * Add: Backups tab file size column (KB/MB)
  * Add: status bar shows tab-context text; Backups tab shows backup count and total size
  * Remove: Addon Versions tab double-click-to-install replaced by explicit action buttons
  * Remove: Backups tab double-click dialog and System ID column removed
  * Add: Accounting tab date range filter (From/To QDateEdit with cross-validation, Last 7d/30d/All time)
  * Add: Accounting tab preview table with full pagination (50 rows/page, prev/next chevron buttons)
  * Add: Accounting tab item names from Wowhead API with disk cache; spinner while loading, i:ID fallback
  * Add: Accounting tab WoW-style item tooltip on hover (quality-colored border, full stat block)
  * Add: Accounting tab gold column: sign-colored number, gold-colored g suffix, auto-sized width
  * Add: Accounting tab summary bar (total sales, purchases, net gold, transactions)
  * Add: Export to CSV now applies the date filter; button shows filtered row count
  * Change: "Accounting Export" tab renamed to "Accounting"
  * Add: status bar GitHub icon (opens repo) and Settings icon (opens dialog), both white on hover
  * Change: status bar text size raised from 10px to 12px
  * Remove: footer bar (Premium and GitHub buttons) replaced by status bar icon buttons
  * Chore: removed dead write_app_info() from AuctionDataService
  * Chore: README sync interval corrected to "5 minutes (differential)"
  * Chore: lua_writer.py docstring corrected; fmt_ts renamed from _fmt_ts

