tsm-app (1.0.4-1) stable; urgency=low

  * Fix: Last Updated column now correctly shows the primary tag timestamp
    (AUCTIONDB_NON_COMMODITY_DATA for realms, AUCTIONDB_REGION_STAT for regions);
    previously a max() fallback could store a wrong timestamp in the snapshot
    when secondary tags were downloaded but the primary tag was not
  * Fix: tray notification text trimmed to "{n} realm(s)/region(s) updated."
  * Add: reverse-engineered TSM API reference document (API.md)
  * CI: softprops/action-gh-release bumped to v2.3.2 (Node.js 24)
  * CI: AUR publishing extracted to a separate manual workflow_dispatch workflow

